{"tid":327540,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不用幫點名了　英文老師好辣！","createTime":"2017-07-19T00:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T01:51:13.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09bf873ff469a6aac562d72a3f237f6672dcbe53","tid":327540,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T00:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170718/420_e5a894d8ad4d70c2f6e2307e0ca818a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170718%2F420_e5a894d8ad4d70c2f6e2307e0ca818a8.jpg&h=5c145765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每到夏天我要去海邊～海邊有個漂亮英文老師(喂)。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170718/420_d4e16610adb21b6b6a0ac3342dc5a6d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170718%2F420_d4e16610adb21b6b6a0ac3342dc5a6d3.jpg&h=0abd119c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聶凡格於影片中舉出幾項常用的水上設施單字，大家有記住嗎？<br />\n<br />\n去年和吳宗憲爆出緋聞，與一名「裸背女」跑飯店，女主角聶凡格知名度因此大開，外貌亮眼的她，163公分，22腰，39公斤卻擁有30D的傲人上圍，身材十分火辣。<br />\n<br />\n性感指數爆表的聶凡格，身穿火辣比基尼授課！正逢暑假期間，很多人會選擇到海邊戲水，甚至出國到其他島嶼國家浮潛，做做日光浴，玩水上活動等等。因應夏季，聶凡格要教大家認識常用的水上設施單字，並將單字運用在句子裡，不囉嗦，現在就開始上課！（影創中心／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>●Emily聶凡格</strong><br />\n<br />\n聶凡格出生成長於美國，大學畢業後回台學習中文，並從事英文教學工作，外界形容為「台灣最正的英文老師」，其網路的英文教學短視頻「ABCDEmily」也擁有高點擊率。後來轉入演藝圈發展，除了出演多部MV、電影、戲劇的拍攝，在各綜藝節目也可以看見她的身影。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/entertainment/20170718/1162851/paperart_right\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fentertainment%2F20170718%2F1162851%2Fpaperart_right&d=caRcr3D7oeYocsrgdcR10sVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=ad7c4cde\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/entertainment/20170718/1162851/paperart_right</a>"},{"pid":"a04fc5d3c467fb3ad88dfbfe7c68d7ca41241b8d","tid":327540,"uid":35701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T00:21:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2da3b82b9763d062a28a6a516f82d0f5fdcd0847","tid":327540,"uid":5302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:51:13.000Z","msg":"39公斤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}